{"word":"ρώμη","slug":"ρώμη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ρώμη</b></el> <el>(ρώμη, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ρώομαι'><el>ρώομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>bodily strength, strength, might</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>οὐ μιᾷ ρώμῃ</el> not single-handed, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a force</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>army</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}